items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Unrelenting if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...

items.name: Forbidden Flesh
explicitMods: Allocates Unrelenting if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flame
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The bodies of those wholly subsumed by the Tangle
continue to merge and mutate and cry out for release...

items.name: Brutal Restraint
explicitMods:
Denoted service of 7050 dekhara in the akhara of Asenath
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Maraketh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves the most ordered, but that tradition turned their forests to salt.
